	<h2><a href="/posts/making-your-regular-expressions-readable:480f4dfe-2d20-4f07-9b83-41bbcbdd56cb">Making your regular expressions readable</a></h2>	<div class="posted-on">
		<p>Posted on 4/5/07 by 
		<a href="/tim">Tim Koschützki</a>				</p>
		<div class="thumb">
			<img alt="" src="/img/tim_thumb.jpg"/>		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="body">
				<p>Today I found a good article on the topic of making one's regular expressions more readable. We often need to use PCRE in our application and they can often get quite long.</p>
